    An Rx-idiomatic expression of Amplify's RestBehavior.

    An Rx idiomatic expression of the facilities in Amplify's StorageCategoryBehavior.
    RxStorageCategoryBehavior.RxStorageTransferCallbackMapper<T>
    Type alias that defines the generic parameters for a download operation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RxAmplify
    A collection of bindings to facilitate use of the Amplify framework with Rx-centered APIs.
    RxOperations
    Top level container class created to hold Rx-specific operation types.
    RxOperations.RxSubscriptionOperation<T>
    A class that represents a subscription operation and exposes observables for consumers to listen to subscription data and status events.
    RxOperations.RxSubscriptionOperation.ConnectionStateEvent
    Describes events emitted by the RxOperations.RxSubscriptionOperation class.
    RxStorageBinding
    Rx binding for Amplify's storage category.
    RxStorageBinding.RxProgressAwareSingleOperation<T>
    A generic implementation of an operation that emits progress information and returns a single.

    Enum representing connection states of a subscription operation.
